body: Hi Taizo, The issue is because you are using an old version of LB HB, if you try to update them your file will work fine. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/-*d*csZ7Ie-19VBBw9ax65d92Nl-O5oS21jd8pfRB2Bsme0cqDOKHVuBRR7NB29j39p1j6abGpfvLh4ThHGP-v*0uyRq83Br/issue_.png) You should use '"Ladybug_Update Ladybug" and "Honeybee_Update Honeybee" to update LB HB. If you are in trouble take a look at here: [http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/error-with-...](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/error-with-comfort-mannequin?commentId=2985220%3AComment%3A1537467&groupId=2985220%3AGroup%3A658987) Best Antonello
